{"name":"2025 全新多维表格仪表盘能力升级","dsl":{"schema":"2.0","config":{"update_multi":true,"style":{"text_size":{"normal_v2":{"default":"normal","pc":"normal","mobile":"heading"}}}},"body":{"direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"12px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","elements":[{"tag":"img","img_key":"IMG_KEY_TODO","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","corner_radius":"8px","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"4 月 22日多维表格 Agent 能力全新升级，已开启本群内测 ✨✨","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":" 只需要动动嘴，AI 就可以帮你搞定数据分析、高级图表可视化和问卷生成","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","flex_mode":"stretch","horizontal_spacing":"12px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","elements":[{"tag":"interactive_container","width":"fill","height":"auto","corner_radius":"4px","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**AI 问数**（模拟）\n能问数让你可以直接用自然语言提问，让 AI 去帮你做筛选、聚合、比较和分析，先把问题的答案拿出来。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"insert-chart_outlined","color":"blue"}}],"has_border":false,"background_style":"blue-100","padding":"4px 4px 4px 6px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"interactive_container","width":"fill","height":"auto","corner_radius":"4px","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**AI 生成仪表盘组件**（模拟）\n只需要说出你的需求，AI 就可以直接把分析结果直接变成更专业的图表组件，比如桑基图、矩形树图、气泡图等，不仅专业，还支持下钻，让复杂关系更容易被看懂。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"insert-chart_outlined","color":"blue"}}],"has_border":false,"background_style":"blue-100","padding":"4px 4px 4px 6px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"interactive_container","width":"fill","height":"auto","corner_radius":"4px","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**AI 生成问卷**（模拟）\nAI 生成问卷可以根据你的自然语言需求，快速生成一份问卷，并把一些常用设置一起配出来。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"insert-chart_outlined","color":"blue"}}],"has_border":false,"background_style":"blue-100","padding":"4px 4px 4px 6px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"padding":"0px 0px 0px 0px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 4px 0px 4px"},{"tag":"interactive_container","width":"fill","height":"auto","corner_radius":"","elements":[],"has_border":false,"padding":"0px 0px 0px 0px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"点击下方按钮**立即加入超前内测**，抢先体验这些新的功能，期待你的反馈建议 💬 ","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"hr","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"button","text":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"立即加入仪表盘内测群 🔥"},"type":"primary_filled","width":"fill","size":"medium","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"team-add_outlined"},"behaviors":[{"type":"open_url","default_url":"HELP_DOC_URL_TODO","pc_url":"HELP_DOC_URL_TODO","ios_url":"HELP_DOC_URL_TODO","android_url":"HELP_DOC_URL_TODO"}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}]},"header":{"title":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"多维表格 2026｜AI 问数、AI 生成组件、AI 生成问卷，邀你体验 🔥🔥"},"subtitle":{"tag":"plain_text","content":""},"text_tag_list":